{"tid":948872,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[大鑊] ASUS、GIGABYTE 驅動程式中遭爆含有權限擴張漏洞！！","createTime":"2018-12-20T11:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T06:00:36.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"56b5588e82f113ee05c29b0f8b1294a65bfaf51e","tid":948872,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:33:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.coolaler.com/threads/asus_gigabyte.353612/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com%2Fthreads%2Fasus_gigabyte.353612%2F&d=Z2jMhz2b9l4CHI9OUTtYFU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=9fe61e87\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.coolaler.com/threads/asus_gigabyte.353612/</a><br />\n<br />\nSecureAuth 旗下的研究單位 SecureAuth Labs 在12月18日的時候發布了 ASUS 以及 GIGABYTE 驅動程式中含有多個涉及權限擴張的安全漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.coolaler.com/proxy.php?image=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F18%2F12%2F122001.jpg&amp;hash=4077fb5daba4b34ac977744efacb1359\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com%2Fproxy.php%3Fimage%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%252Fimage%252Fnews%252F18%252F12%252F122001.jpg%26hash%3D4077fb5daba4b34ac977744efacb1359&h=bb240098&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9c44cf3f3f93f21c0f0ba0551e5d9cad87397e7","tid":948872,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"ASUS Aura Sync 燈效同步軟體所安裝的 GLCKIo 與 Asusgio 驅動程式中含有3個安全漏洞，將允許本地端駭客擴張權限並執行任意程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，其中 GLCKIo 含有 CVE-2018-18537 與 CVE-2018-18536 兩個安全漏洞，前者可造系統當機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，後者可能允許本地端駭客執行任意程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，Asusgio 則含有 CVE-2018-18536 及 CVE-2018-18535 兩個安全漏洞，後者可以最高權限執行任意程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\nSecureAuth Labs 表示去年17年11月就已經與 ASUS 接洽，不過到今年1月才得到 ASUS 的回應，儘管 ASUS 在今年5月前曾經兩度更新 Aura Sync，但僅修補其中一個驅動程式的安全漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n至於 GIGIABYTE 的漏洞則是存在於主機板及顯卡上用到的 GPCIDrv 與 GDrv 兩款驅動程式，相關的漏洞編號分別為 CVE-2018-19320、CVE-2018-19322、CVE-2018-19323 與CVE-2018-19321，允許駭客重新啟動系統、執行任意程式或掌控整個系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\nSecureAuth Labs 則是在今年4月與 GIGABYTE 聯繫，但 GIGABYTE 的技術團隊曾多次以 GIGABYTE 為硬體公司、並不專精軟體為由，要求該實驗室提供更詳細的技術資料，更在7月說該公司的產品經理及工程師認為 GIGABYTE 的產品並未受到相關漏洞的影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"d273c00175b053085349b74f4f18ecf4303c6a6b","tid":948872,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:37:26.000Z","msg":"SecureAuth Labs 在本周同時公布了華碩與技嘉驅動程式的漏洞細節，詳細可以參考以下連結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secureauth.com/labs/advisories/asus-drivers-elevation-privilege-vulnerabilities\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secureauth.com%2Flabs%2Fadvisories%2Fasus-drivers-elevation-privilege-vulnerabilities&d=Z2jMhz2b9l4CHI9OUTtYFU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=10ec382a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secureauth.com/labs/advisories/asus-drivers-elevation-privilege-vulnerabilities</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secureauth.com/labs/advisories/gigabyte-drivers-elevation-privilege-vulnerabilities\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secureauth.com%2Flabs%2Fadvisories%2Fgigabyte-drivers-elevation-privilege-vulnerabilities&d=Z2jMhz2b9l4CHI9OUTtYFU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a48ce4c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secureauth.com/labs/advisories/gigabyte-drivers-elevation-privilege-vulnerabilities</a>"},{"pid":"462f51feeb625634d326ffd885515690dda24112","tid":948872,"uid":95172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88835260730f71b0470e6d7b032edbb4a29a62a1","tid":948872,"uid":1886,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"MSI 用家到此一遊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a973d286a71fae6ece746b23a96fe120bf71712","tid":948872,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">ASROCK 都有份</span></span></strong><br />\n不過人哋一早就fix好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/others/56219/secureauth-labs-asus-gigabyte-privilege-vulnerabilities/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fothers%2F56219%2Fsecureauth-labs-asus-gigabyte-privilege-vulnerabilities%2F&d=Z2jMhz2b9l4CHI9OUTtYFU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=fdab6934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/others/56219/secureauth-labs-asus-gigabyte-privilege-vulnerabilities/</a><br />\n<br />\n目前狀態是華碩已修復其中一項漏洞，但並未完全防範這安全問題；而技嘉方面：「Gigabyte responded that, according to its PM and engineers, its products are not affected by the reported vulnerabilities.」。<br />\n<br />\n查閱 SecureAuth Labs 的資料，ASRock 已經在 2018-08-16 就完成類似安全漏洞的修正並回報；若各位玩家擔心電腦資料安全疑慮，建議可先將上述提到的應用程式移除，待日後更新再安裝。"},{"pid":"fad903ef2aa9fbb468419655b7a3d68ddcb41c21","tid":948872,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:11:12.000Z","msg":"我愛msi"},{"pid":"964d4ada69b023eb559fbe3e273b34ad98f5aae2","tid":9